cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual speech recognition using 3D feature extraction methods. 
2. cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with identifying phonemes and visemes from continuous speech. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses Support Vector Machines and Hidden Markov Models for classification. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition and language processing. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with video processing and feature extraction.
